title: Udemy Blog Traffic Tactics: Create A Huge Following In 9 Steps
description:
Description

Do You Want To Build A Huge Following On Your Blog And Make A Tonne Of Passive Income? Building A Blog Is Easy. The Hard Part? Building A Huge Audience.Thats where I come in. My name is Daniel Boehm and I’ve been blogging since 2008, and currently make a full time income online. The biggest worries I had when I started my first blog was, “How do I get people here? I need people to make money, and I don’t have time writing article after article and “hoping” that people find me.

If you have the same doubts and worries, then this course is for you.

For years I struggled with getting traffic to my site, trying all kinds of cheap tactics and wrong advice that eventually got my site penalised on search engines.

Who is the target audience?

    This traffic generation course is designed for people who want to build a huge audience to their site, whether you have a brand new site or are struggling to get traffic to a site you’ve already built.

Requirements

    Students won’t need any materials or software, the information in this course covers everything they need. As long as you have a website, then this course will show you how to bring in a huge audience
